WEBVTT

00:08.791 --> 00:10.791
[pulsing music playing]

00:32.916 --> 00:34.916
♪ ♪

00:50.041 --> 00:52.041
[atmospheric music playing]

01:08.708 --> 01:10.916
[gasping]

01:12.625 --> 01:13.957
[gasps]

01:13.958 --> 01:16.207
- [inner voices whisper indistinctly]
- Please.

01:16.208 --> 01:18.415
[panting]

01:18.416 --> 01:20.291
[rustling]

01:26.541 --> 01:28.707
- [Ahokal] It's a human boy.
- [gasps]

01:28.708 --> 01:30.624
[Tally] A kid? What's he doing here?

01:30.625 --> 01:32.999
[Luzum] Well, he's in a cage.
He's either in trouble

01:33.000 --> 01:34.290
or he is trouble.

01:34.291 --> 01:36.832
[Mora] We have to assume
the former, Luzum.

01:36.833 --> 01:38.415
We're a rescue party now.

01:38.416 --> 01:40.582
[suspenseful music playing]

01:40.583 --> 01:42.666
- [inner voices echoing]
- [groans]

01:44.583 --> 01:47.707
[Mora] These are hallowed lands
of the Loyal Fury.

01:47.708 --> 01:50.040
- [blades sliding out of sheaths]
- Protected by the great Oriel.

01:50.041 --> 01:52.916
- We offer you one chance--
- [cultist yells]

01:54.791 --> 01:56.790
- [grunting]
- [Tally] Follow my lead!

01:56.791 --> 01:58.791
[Ahokal] Tally, no fire.

02:02.125 --> 02:04.040
[roars]

02:04.041 --> 02:06.125
[dramatic music playing]

02:12.791 --> 02:16.375
[inner voices] <i>It matters not!
You are mine.</i>

02:22.166 --> 02:24.166
[calm music playing]

02:29.458 --> 02:31.625
[grunts]

02:39.583 --> 02:41.583
[ominous music playing]

02:52.833 --> 02:55.082
[gasping]

02:55.083 --> 02:58.000
W-Who are you? What do you want with me?

03:02.291 --> 03:04.040
It's all right. We're safe.

03:04.041 --> 03:05.499
My name is Mora.

03:05.500 --> 03:08.415
You were a prisoner
of The Cult of the Dragon.

03:08.416 --> 03:10.332
We're taking you to Oriel
to cure you of your affliction.

03:10.333 --> 03:12.582
Whoa, whoa, whoa.
You don't know he's not one of them.

03:12.583 --> 03:14.249
- He wasn't--
- How do you know?

03:14.250 --> 03:17.582
- No, no, no.
- Those tattoos looks like
somebody ripped him out

03:17.583 --> 03:18.957
- of the Book of Vile Darkness.
- No, no. Leave me alone.

03:18.958 --> 03:21.374
- Tally, leave it.
- You're in terrible danger.

03:21.375 --> 03:22.957
Are you a cultist, kid?

03:22.958 --> 03:26.332
Tally, the tattoos mark him for sacrifice.

03:26.333 --> 03:29.290
I'd venture they were taking him
to the Well of Dragons.

03:29.291 --> 03:31.415
[scoffs] Marvelous.

03:31.416 --> 03:33.915
[Luzum] Probably to be sacrificed
to Tiamat.

03:33.916 --> 03:34.999
[inner voices speaking indistinctly]

03:35.000 --> 03:36.332
We're going to help you.

03:36.333 --> 03:38.124
No. No, no. Stay back. Stay back.

03:38.125 --> 03:39.665
- She's coming
- It's okay.

03:39.666 --> 03:40.958
She's coming!

03:41.875 --> 03:44.749
- [inner voices] <i>Amid astahii!</i>
- [Luzum] Mora! Mora!

03:44.750 --> 03:46.582
- [Tally] How did he move so fast?
- I'm sorry.

03:46.583 --> 03:47.999
- I-I didn't...
- [Tally] I knew it.

03:48.000 --> 03:51.332
- You're gonna burn, kid.
- [Mora] Stop.

03:51.333 --> 03:54.415
[labored breathing]

03:54.416 --> 03:56.707
[pained grunt]

03:56.708 --> 03:59.082
[gentle music playing]

03:59.083 --> 04:00.875
I've had worse.

04:03.250 --> 04:05.457
Come with me, kid.

04:05.458 --> 04:07.083
Mora...

04:08.375 --> 04:10.999
[Mora] We just need a minute alone.

04:11.000 --> 04:13.541
What we need is a cleric.

04:16.250 --> 04:18.250
[gentle music playing]

04:26.625 --> 04:28.416
What is your name, child?

04:29.416 --> 04:31.624
Solon.

04:31.625 --> 04:34.874
I think you didn't mean to hurt me, Solon.

04:34.875 --> 04:38.165
Whatever is in you, it's strong,
but I can see

04:38.166 --> 04:41.165
- you are strong, too.
- [inner voices] <i>Lies! Lies!</i>

04:41.166 --> 04:42.832
<i>Lies! Lies!</i>

04:42.833 --> 04:44.749
<i>Lies!</i>

04:44.750 --> 04:46.916
[panting]

04:48.250 --> 04:50.374
You should listen to the others.

04:50.375 --> 04:52.999
Just... leave me.

04:53.000 --> 04:55.166
- It'll be easier for all of us.
- Maybe.

04:56.250 --> 04:57.999
Being easier doesn't make it right.

04:58.000 --> 05:01.124
[gentle music playing]

05:01.125 --> 05:02.875
I wasn't always a Paladin of Torm.

05:04.708 --> 05:07.166
Most of these scars
are from fights I started.

05:09.458 --> 05:14.832
I very nearly killed innocents
before I decided to change.

05:14.833 --> 05:16.208
Before I took my oath.

05:18.041 --> 05:21.708
But that person who did those things...

05:23.041 --> 05:24.833
...that's still me.

05:27.000 --> 05:29.457
Now, that's who I fight.

05:29.458 --> 05:32.665
Every hour of every day.

05:32.666 --> 05:35.165
[melancholy music playing]

05:35.166 --> 05:37.958
I don't always win.

05:40.166 --> 05:43.082
It reminds me I'm not alone.

05:43.083 --> 05:45.749
Maybe it will help you.

05:45.750 --> 05:48.333
Hold on to it until you reach Oriel.

05:49.416 --> 05:51.374
[Ahokal whistles]

05:51.375 --> 05:53.665
They found us.

05:53.666 --> 05:55.625
[growling]

05:57.625 --> 06:00.165
[intense music playing]

06:00.166 --> 06:01.415
You really think this...

06:01.416 --> 06:03.625
Oriel will know how to help me?

06:06.208 --> 06:08.208
[dramatic music playing]

06:36.791 --> 06:39.208
- Hurry!
- Quiet! I need to focus.

06:42.208 --> 06:44.250
[horses whinnying]

06:55.583 --> 06:57.791
What in the Nine Hells-- [grunts]

07:01.583 --> 07:04.040
[grunts]

07:04.041 --> 07:05.874
Oh...

07:05.875 --> 07:08.165
Mora, get him inside.

07:08.166 --> 07:10.750
We'll hold them off.

07:12.750 --> 07:14.582
Good luck, kid.

07:14.583 --> 07:16.916
[dramatic music playing]

07:23.041 --> 07:25.416
[inner voices whispering indistinctly]

07:26.541 --> 07:28.540
- [inner voices continues whispering]
- [hisses] No, no, no.

07:28.541 --> 07:30.582
We have to go. We have to leave now.

07:30.583 --> 07:32.832
[Mora] It's going to be okay.

07:32.833 --> 07:34.916
[dramatic music playing]

07:41.625 --> 07:44.582
Oriel, this is Solon.

07:44.583 --> 07:47.290
He bears a terrible curse.

07:47.291 --> 07:50.124
Calm yourself, child.

07:50.125 --> 07:52.290
You're safe here.

07:52.291 --> 07:53.750
[Solon] She's getting loud.

07:56.291 --> 07:58.874
[inner voices] <i>Oriesj C'hazh. Rhyst ah.
Rhyst ah plythu.</i>

07:58.875 --> 08:00.290
No, no stay back.

08:00.291 --> 08:04.207
This thing inside me
doesn't like you at all.

08:04.208 --> 08:05.707
[Oriel chuckles]

08:05.708 --> 08:08.415
The wicked do tend to fear me.

08:08.416 --> 08:11.707
I will take whatever is inside you

08:11.708 --> 08:13.290
and destroy it.

08:13.291 --> 08:16.915
I... don’t want it to hurt you.

08:16.916 --> 08:21.124
Your kindness is precisely
what makes you worthy

08:21.125 --> 08:23.333
of being freed.

08:24.583 --> 08:26.874
[wind whistling]

08:26.875 --> 08:28.958
- [suspenseful music playing]
- They're coming through.

08:30.500 --> 08:32.125
[Luzum] Incoming!

08:33.125 --> 08:34.166
[cries out]

08:35.166 --> 08:38.000
[Ahokal] Tally, we need fire!

08:40.625 --> 08:42.791
[Tally] Okay. Get out of the way.
Here we go.

08:45.166 --> 08:46.332
[low growl]

08:46.333 --> 08:48.915
[inner voice] They don't know
what they're doing.

08:48.916 --> 08:52.666
There are too many. Tally, no!

08:56.708 --> 08:58.624
[inhales]

08:58.625 --> 09:00.791
[ominous music playing]

09:08.750 --> 09:10.916
[grunts, gasps]

09:15.750 --> 09:17.708
[fighters grunting]

09:31.000 --> 09:32.750
Tally.

09:34.041 --> 09:36.125
[screeching]

09:38.916 --> 09:40.458
[screeches]

09:51.166 --> 09:53.166
[inhales]

09:58.666 --> 10:00.207
Fire! Now!

10:00.208 --> 10:04.000
[Solon cries out]

10:08.125 --> 10:09.707
Finally.

10:09.708 --> 10:11.791
[grunts]

10:15.166 --> 10:18.040
[inner voices] <i>Astahii plythu nah.</i>

10:18.041 --> 10:22.250
<i>Loaw tah nah! Plythu tah! Vorae...</i>

10:23.625 --> 10:25.332
[pained cry]

10:25.333 --> 10:26.791
[Solon's cry echoing]

10:28.041 --> 10:29.625
[grunts]

10:34.000 --> 10:35.915
[mournful music playing]

10:35.916 --> 10:38.750
[Mora] Solon. Solon, say something.

10:40.875 --> 10:42.125
It's...

10:44.833 --> 10:46.375
...quiet.

10:59.833 --> 11:02.083
[coughing]

11:04.333 --> 11:06.124
[pained roar]

11:06.125 --> 11:08.500
Whatever this is, it's loud.

11:10.083 --> 11:12.082
Unpleasant.

11:12.083 --> 11:16.165
You carried this in you for years...

11:16.166 --> 11:18.665
Impressive.

11:18.666 --> 11:21.207
[inner voices] Every dragon...

11:21.208 --> 11:25.082
is a gateway...

11:25.083 --> 11:27.790
[Oriel] I-I can't...

11:27.791 --> 11:30.290
hold it in.

11:30.291 --> 11:33.290
Run. Run!

11:33.291 --> 11:35.583
[intense music playing]

12:06.250 --> 12:07.458
[Mora] Gods.

12:17.666 --> 12:20.915
That's a whole lot of dragon.

12:20.916 --> 12:22.583
Tiamat.

12:29.166 --> 12:30.750
[grunts]

12:36.958 --> 12:40.332
Well, guess we found our cleric.

12:40.333 --> 12:42.415
Go.

12:42.416 --> 12:44.374
I've been fighting her my whole life.

12:44.375 --> 12:46.082
I can hold her back on my own.

12:46.083 --> 12:48.291
I believe you could...

12:50.375 --> 12:52.208
...but you're not on your own.

12:58.750 --> 12:59.750
[grunts]

13:00.750 --> 13:01.915
[Mora huffs]

13:01.916 --> 13:03.624
[Luzum grunting]

13:03.625 --> 13:05.541
[hisses]

13:08.458 --> 13:10.375
[growling]

13:12.500 --> 13:14.500
[gentle music playing]

13:44.125 --> 13:46.125
♪ ♪

14:16.375 --> 14:18.375
♪ ♪
